353
00:29:58,637 --> 00:30:02,725
#Kimse bizi kızartıp yemez

354
00:30:03,601 --> 00:30:06,229
#Karada ise durum başka

355
00:30:06,312 --> 00:30:08,690
#Denizin dibinde, oltalardan uzakta

356
00:30:08,773 --> 00:30:11,277
#Belaya bulaşmayız

357
00:30:11,360 --> 00:30:13,361
#Denizin dibinde
